---
title: Creamy Broccoli Curry with sprinkled scallions and rice
description: Though it may be a snap to make, this isn't your ordinary curry in a hurry. Loads of veggies, cubes of golden fried cheese, lashings of rich and creamy sauce... what more could you want?
